A '''spleen''' was an organ that several organisms possessed, including [[Human/Legends|Humans]] and [[Dianoga/Legends|dianogas]].

Spleens could rupture or suffer from [[spleen-rot]]. [[Dianogan tea/Legends|Dianogan tea]] was made from the spleens of dianogas.

During the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Anakin Solo]] was critically injured when his spleen was ruptured. The internal [[Blood/Legends|bleeding]] caused by the organ's perforation led to his [[Death/Legends|death]].<ref name="sbs">''[[The New Jedi Order: Star by Star]]''</ref>

